1
00:00:29,530 --> 00:00:30,930
Madam, in the Gu family,

2
00:00:31,260 --> 00:00:33,260
are you getting used to living here?

3
00:00:33,630 --> 00:00:35,560
Naturally, I am used to it.

4
00:00:36,130 --> 00:00:36,930
That's good.

5
00:00:37,660 --> 00:00:39,730
The Gu family naturally cannot compare to the Immortal Realm.

6
00:00:39,730 --> 00:00:41,830
If there is anything you are not used to,

7
00:00:41,830 --> 00:00:43,560
you can just tell the servants.

8
00:00:45,330 --> 00:00:46,000
No wonder.

9
00:00:46,730 --> 00:00:48,100
I was wondering why this guy

10
00:00:48,100 --> 00:00:51,100
would take a mortal woman as a concubine for no reason.

11
00:00:52,360 --> 00:00:53,830
So this Lu Wanqing

12
00:00:54,030 --> 00:00:56,090
is actually from the Immortal Realm.

13
00:00:56,160 --> 00:00:57,700
Immortal Realm or not,

14
00:00:57,830 --> 00:01:00,230
I am now just my husband's concubine.

15
00:01:00,230 --> 00:01:01,000
Don't worry.

16
00:01:01,300 --> 00:01:02,460
For Madam's sake,

17
00:01:02,660 --> 00:01:04,060
I won't do anything to Su Yao.

18
00:01:04,060 --> 00:01:06,060
Seeing her cultivating at the Taixuan Holy Land recently,

19
00:01:06,060 --> 00:01:07,030
she is quite diligent.

20
00:01:07,030 --> 00:01:08,230
You are generous, my husband,

21
00:01:08,230 --> 00:01:11,030
but I'm afraid that girl Yao'er doesn't think so.

22
00:01:15,260 --> 00:01:17,760
The Human Emperor's edict has arrived!

23
00:01:18,060 --> 00:01:19,730
Gu Linyuan, the guard of the Gu family,

24
00:01:19,730 --> 00:01:22,330
get out here immediately to receive the edict!

25
00:01:28,130 --> 00:01:31,230
Old Demon Gu has offended the Human Ancestral Court in the Central State.

26
00:01:31,230 --> 00:01:32,500
It's actually true.

27
00:01:32,700 --> 00:01:36,060
I heard that the major Human Emperor families jointly impeached him.

28
00:01:36,060 --> 00:01:38,700
Old Demon Gu snatched the Xiao family's Imperial Weapon

29
00:01:38,700 --> 00:01:40,830
and casually killed their patriarch.

30
00:01:42,060 --> 00:01:43,030
Crazy, he's completely crazy.

31
00:01:43,030 --> 00:01:44,030
Let's go, let's go and have a look.

32
00:01:44,030 --> 00:01:44,690
Patriarch.

33
00:01:44,759 --> 00:01:46,330
How dare the Human Ancestral Court

34
00:01:46,330 --> 00:01:48,360
let their envoy block the gate of our Gu family,

35
00:01:48,360 --> 00:01:50,330
and ask our dignified Quasi-emperor to receive the edict!

36
00:01:50,330 --> 00:01:51,990
What a Human Ancestral Court!

37
00:01:52,229 --> 00:01:53,560
So shameless

38
00:01:53,700 --> 00:01:54,960
to put the blame on the victim!

39
00:01:54,960 --> 00:01:58,130
They clearly intended to slaughter the innocents in the Sin Village

40
00:01:58,130 --> 00:01:59,860
and suppress our Master first.

41
00:02:00,030 --> 00:02:01,730
They were killed because they were inferior,

42
00:02:01,730 --> 00:02:04,160
and now they hold a grudge against our Master.

43
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:05,090
Let's eat first.

44
00:02:06,300 --> 00:02:07,430
Where is Gu Linyuan?

45
00:02:07,860 --> 00:02:10,259
Come here and kneel down to receive the Ancestral Court's edict immediately!

46
00:02:10,259 --> 00:02:11,230
This envoy of the Ancestral Court

47
00:02:11,230 --> 00:02:12,600
has such a great air of authority.

48
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:14,200
A mere Ascension Realm cultivator,

49
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,300
not even a Saint,

50
00:02:15,530 --> 00:02:17,560
dares to ask a current Quasi-emperor to receive the edict,

51
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,490
and on his knees!

52
00:02:18,530 --> 00:02:19,190
Is he crazy,

53
00:02:19,260 --> 00:02:20,760
or does he think he has lived too long?

54
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:21,430
Gu Linyuan,

55
00:02:21,829 --> 00:02:23,329
show yourself immediately!

56
00:02:23,329 --> 00:02:25,460
If you dare to disobey the Ancestral Court's edict,

57
00:02:25,460 --> 00:02:27,000
it is a betrayal of the entire human race.

58
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:28,100
You will fall into darkness,

59
00:02:28,100 --> 00:02:29,460
become a tainted bloodline,

60
00:02:29,460 --> 00:02:30,860
and be doomed eternally!

61
00:02:31,230 --> 00:02:32,160
What did

62
00:02:32,660 --> 00:02:33,390
you just say?

63
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:36,700
Her Majesty the Empress orders you

64
00:02:36,700 --> 00:02:38,860
to go to the Ancestral Court immediately to plead guilty,

65
00:02:38,860 --> 00:02:40,100
return the Xiao Clan's Imperial Weapon,

66
00:02:40,100 --> 00:02:42,100
and kneel down to receive the edict!

67
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:42,829
What realm

68
00:02:43,300 --> 00:02:44,300
am I?

69
00:02:45,060 --> 00:02:46,160
A Quasi-Emperor.

70
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,500
Then what realm

71
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:48,620
is your Empress in?

72
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:50,900
Her Majesty the Empress is the youngest

73
00:02:50,900 --> 00:02:52,300
Saint realm expert in the history of the Tianxuan Continent,

74
00:02:52,300 --> 00:02:53,160
the chosen one.

75
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:53,560
Oh,

76
00:02:53,660 --> 00:02:54,120
so she is

77
00:02:54,329 --> 00:02:55,500
just at the ant realm.

78
00:02:55,500 --> 00:02:56,760
You are yelling today,

79
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,630
trying to make me, a dignified Quasi-Emperor,

80
00:02:58,630 --> 00:03:00,290
kneel and apologize to an ant?

81
00:03:00,430 --> 00:03:01,000
Just because

82
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:02,330
she is the Human Empress?

83
00:03:02,330 --> 00:03:03,990
You bold fanatic, Gu Linyuan!

84
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,030
Although you are a Quasi-Emperor,

85
00:03:05,030 --> 00:03:06,560
you still have human blood.

86
00:03:06,730 --> 00:03:07,930
You should revere the Ancestral Court

87
00:03:07,930 --> 00:03:09,060
and obey the decree.

88
00:03:09,200 --> 00:03:10,060
If you disrespect the Human Emperor,

89
00:03:10,060 --> 00:03:12,500
you are an eternal traitor to the human race.

90
00:03:12,500 --> 00:03:12,960
Noisy.

91
00:03:18,260 --> 00:03:19,920
Go back and tell your Empress,

92
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,430
I

93
00:03:21,900 --> 00:03:23,030
don't eat beef.

94
00:03:23,230 --> 00:03:24,329
An envoy of the Ancestral Court,

95
00:03:24,329 --> 00:03:25,800
killed just like that,

96
00:03:25,829 --> 00:03:27,360
and even his ashes are scattered.

97
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,290
This old demon Gu

98
00:03:28,530 --> 00:03:30,260
is as fierce as ever.

99
00:03:30,300 --> 00:03:32,630
The Human Ancestral Court indeed went too far.

100
00:03:32,630 --> 00:03:33,500
In any case,

101
00:03:33,860 --> 00:03:36,630
making a current Quasi-Emperor kneel to receive a decree.

102
00:03:36,630 --> 00:03:37,690
Such humiliation,

103
00:03:38,060 --> 00:03:39,760
they brought it upon themselves.

104
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:41,420
It's not peaceful these days.

105
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:43,760
I heard there was chaos at the Imperial Pass a few days ago.

106
00:03:43,760 --> 00:03:46,000
Luo Jinghong, the Luo Clan's Quasi-Emperor in charge of guarding,

107
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:46,760
suddenly went mad,

108
00:03:46,760 --> 00:03:48,100
slaughtered the inspector for no reason,

109
00:03:48,100 --> 00:03:49,060
and then left through the void,

110
00:03:49,060 --> 00:03:49,960
whereabouts unknown.

111
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,960
The Human Ancestral Court announced to the world long ago

112
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,800
that the Luo Clan's Quasi-Emperor colluded with the Demon Clan

113
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:54,700
and betrayed the human race.

114
00:03:54,700 --> 00:03:56,300
The newly succeeded Jiang Yun

115
00:03:56,300 --> 00:03:57,860
is so ruthless,

116
00:03:58,130 --> 00:04:01,330
truly inheriting the methods of the major Human Emperor families.

117
00:04:01,330 --> 00:04:02,530
Rumor has it that

118
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:05,100
old demon Gu went to the Central State this time

119
00:04:05,100 --> 00:04:06,800
to raid that Sin Village

120
00:04:07,260 --> 00:04:09,590
and took away the remnants of the Luo Clan.

121
00:04:09,860 --> 00:04:11,130
That's what caused the crazy counterattack from the Ancestral Court

122
00:04:11,130 --> 00:04:13,460
and the major Human Emperor families.

123
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:17,399
We shouldn't wade into this muddy water.

124
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:18,329
Let's slip away.

125
00:04:19,700 --> 00:04:20,959
The food is still warm.

126
00:04:21,459 --> 00:04:22,029
Sit down

127
00:04:22,530 --> 00:04:23,730
and continue eating.

128
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:24,260
Master.

129
00:04:24,930 --> 00:04:27,160
This Human Ancestral Court is simply too much.

130
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,000
Confusing right and wrong,

131
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,060
distorting the facts,

132
00:04:29,060 --> 00:04:30,760
pushing the Luo Clan to a dead end,

133
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:32,659
and now they dare to humiliate you like this.

134
00:04:32,659 --> 00:04:35,720
They don't deserve to be the orthodox human race at all.

135
00:04:35,760 --> 00:04:37,760
It seems the human race has been at peace for too long,

136
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:38,800
their rules are completely rotten.

137
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:40,530
We might as well return to the Immemorial Era

138
00:04:40,530 --> 00:04:41,960
and let the Immemorial Myriad Races

139
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:43,600
rule this land again.

140
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:44,760
Patriarch.

141
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:46,460
Autumn is here.

142
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,060
It's getting cold,

143
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:50,100
put on a yellow robe.
